                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110403-77-off455 t18110403-77-cd456"></join>, thirty pounds weight of lead, value 5 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18110403-77-victim740" type="victimName">
                           Matthew 
